{"tid":853601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［人無恥則無敵］大家有無遇過呢種同學？入黎評下理","createTime":"2018-10-08T17:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T17:27:42.000Z","uid":215563,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ca7a835ca6e3ebe9eb61492ea85bb699484ff7","tid":853601,"uid":215563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"話說今年year 2<br />\n過幾日之後要交一份assignment<br />\n佔分好重<br />\n咁上個禮拜我就請教一個師兄解答下唔明嘅問題<br />\n之後佢好好人介紹埋一個app俾我<br />\n裡面有好多資料解答到好多呢科一d好難嘅concept<br />\n<br />\n跟住前幾日我就同個同學溫書<br />\n咁佢就問我關於嗰科嘅問題，之後我就用個app解俾佢知<br />\n<br />\n點知到左夜晚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢係我地班group share個app出去叫所有人去down<br />\n之後話好有用 可以幫大家解答到個科既問題<br />\n但完全無話係其他人介紹俾佢<br />\n講到好似自己搵到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己攞曬彩<br />\n然後其他同學當佢神咁拜<br />\n<br />\n我依家好後悔話個app俾佢知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認為同學為搏出位攞彩行為可恥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好計較同學大愛嘅行為"},{"pid":"789abb70864a6374869ac9bd74cab80d54f3f04d","tid":853601,"uid":171509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:07:28.000Z","msg":"而家成個連登都知道你勁咪得囉<br />\n咁都搵到個咁有用既app<br />\n真心 消點解你咁犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a11f94cce7e2e5455263dab85972b71b772749","tid":853601,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:22:03.000Z","msg":"都係師兄介紹畀你㗎啫<br />\n唔順氣咪上group講<br />\n話係人哋介紹畀你<br />\n你再介紹畀佢囉<br />\n再者，你有心一早share嘅<br />\n攞彩嘅咪你囉<br />\n收埋收埋<br />\n然後人哋懶大方你就唔gur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b22cf1f995a6f0a915ecd5ddee6ed69d087a06","tid":853601,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:22:30.000Z","msg":"btw 投你老母票"},{"pid":"e2fe8e94d8912530a93e4eaefd63b00ea66fb384","tid":853601,"uid":36072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:27:42.000Z","msg":"樓主今舖柒哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住有張底牌今科A硬<br />\n點知揚咗出去變大家一齊A<br />\n人人考第一咪即係人人都包尾<br />\n下次有好野記得收好D啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算想幫人都隱蔽d咁開個apps呀嘛"}]}